{"header":"<h1>Parameter <code><span>Prod2.B1</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"codex","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Datatype_sig","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Prod2","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"B1","href":"#","kind":"argument-1"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-t\"><a href=\"#type-t\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> t</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-equal\"><a href=\"#val-equal\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> equal : <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> bool</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Any notion of equality is allowed, as long as it is an equivalence relation, and that if <code>a == b</code>, then <code>equal a b</code>.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-compare\"><a href=\"#val-compare\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> compare : <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> int</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>compare</code> is a total order, and should be compatible with equal.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-hash\"><a href=\"#val-hash\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> hash : <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> int</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>hash</code> requires that equal values have the same hash.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-pretty\"><a href=\"#val-pretty\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> pretty : <span><span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Stdlib</span>.Format.formatter <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div></div>"}